ACTRESS Kgomotso Christopher has scored a TV presenting gig on SABC2's Raising Babies 101. Entertainment reporter Phil Mphela shared the news via Twitter. He said Kgomotso will be hosting the Tuesday edition focusing on toddlers. The show airs Monday to Wednesday at 9am. Kgomotso recently left Etv's Scandal and joined M-Net telenovela Legacy. Also read: LIVING MY DREAM LIKE I DON’T CARE 